<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>5. Check the brake actuator assembly with the intelligent tester. (Check brake actuator assembly operation using the Active Test function.) If abnormal, check the hydraulic circuit for leakage.</ptxt>
