<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>6. If the symptoms still occur even after the above circuits in suspected areas have been inspected and proved to be normal, replace the brake actuator assembly (skid control ECU).</ptxt>
